   tiers:[{label:"Reactive",upTo:2},{label:"Composed",upTo:5},{label:"Unflinching",upTo:8}],
   why:"Mental fortitude is the inner steadiness to stay calm, clear, and in control of yourself when conditions are hostile — fear, fatigue, chaos, discomfort. It is the anchor beneath leadership and performance, and it is trainable through deliberate exposure.",
