   "Reach L2: use INNER and LEFT JOIN to query related tables; explain NULL handling.",
   "Reach L3: write GROUP BY with aggregates and use subqueries.",
   "Reach L4: design a 3NF normalized schema for a 5-entity system.",
   "Reach L5: write complex queries with CTEs or window functions like ROW_NUMBER and LAG.",
